casebody.data:
Andrew KANE, Individually and as Personal Representative of the Estate of Andrew Dwayne Cornish, petitioner,
v.
Brian LEWIS, et al. No. 15-193. Supreme Court of the United States Oct. 19, 2015.

Motion of Seth Stoughton for leave to file a brief as amicus curiae granted. Motion of Cato Institute for leave to file a brief as amicus curiae granted. Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Fourth Circuit denied.
